umd.cs.shop2
Class TaskAtom

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--umd.cs.shop2.TaskAtom
public class TaskAtom
extends java.lang.Object

A task plus the arguments for that task. Examples: (!put block1 block2), (move-tower (block1 block2 block3) block4). Used as an input to the Shop constructor for embedded use). Also used as the content of the TaskNode elements of the tree returned by SHOP2.
